"<1.so>The <2.se_co>Igneo Talus <3.re_co>is a huge beast whose\n"
"body is made of lava. There are a few of\n"
"'em around <4.se_co>Goron City<5.re_co>.\n"
"I defeated a whole lot of 'em, but no\n"
"matter how hard I try, I can't reach\n"
"the <6.se_co>Igneo Talus <7.re_co>at <8.se_co>Darunia Lake<9.re_co>."
msgstr ""

